title: Little Devil Teemo Icon
body: I won a match of Doom Bots of Doom! I didn't disconnect! So when is the last day when u can recive it , it will be like a trophy for me so please someone tell me! Rito pls! {{champion:17}} {{summoner:14}} {{sticker:slayer-pantheon-rainbows}}

replies.body:
We're sending these Icons out over time and the last day to receive these icons is on November 17th. If you don't have it by then, hit us up in a [support ticket.](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new)

Let me know if you have any questions.
